			<p>Kenny,</p>
<p>For the yellow rocker &amp; shelf, I already had those on hand from decorating our previous apartment, which is why I didn&#8217;t talk about them so much. I just went to Home Depot &amp; searched for a true yellow wood stain. Turns out you can have the guys at the paint counter mix custom wood stain colors for you. I just had them mix up a batch of Minwax water-based yellow stain for me. The color is a true yellow, nothin&#8217; special.</p>
	            
								
